B.ML=new A.at(B.iu,["acupuncture",u.b,"Acupuncture Training","6 Months","Beginner \u2013 Advanced","Limited Seats","A comprehensive hands-on training program covering traditional acupuncture theory, meridian systems, needle techniques, and clinical applications. Participants will gain the knowledge and practical skills to safely perform acupuncture therapy.",B.Jp],t.yf)
B.Jf=s(["History & Islamic perspective of Hijama","Dry & wet cupping techniques","Hygiene & sterilisation standards","Point selection for common conditions","Hands-on practical sessions","Certificate upon completion"],t.s)
B.MO=new A.at(B.iu,["cupping",u.k,"Hijama / Cupping Therapy Training","6 Month","All Levels","Limited Seats","Learn the ancient art of Hijama (wet cupping) and dry cupping therapy in a safe, hygienic, and professional setting. This course covers the historical roots, therapeutic benefits, safety protocols, and step-by-step clinical procedures.",B.Jf],t.yf)
